{"tid":1336112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想再遊行多次尖沙咀","createTime":"2019-07-20T19:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T19:23:23.000Z","uid":274441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47c107c11696c4c95222b708f81d1923c2a239ba","tid":1336112,"uid":274441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:23:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我好贊成遊九龍多過港島</span></span><br />\n1. 夜晚都有小巴走<br />\n2. 尖沙咀同旺角真係最多最多大陸人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係想光復多次尖沙咀<br />\n上次行到名店街<br />\n我個心真係好爽<br />\n<br />\n我地既敵人吾係大陸人，但做得幾多得幾多，大陸消息一面倒話我地搞<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港獨</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>一係就資訊封閉晒。<br />\n我要比佢地知我地呢個幾月香港人其實爭取緊咩野<br />\n宣單加同佢地傾計係work"}]}